    "axos": "<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">               ▂🬭𜴧⎻𜷗𜴗𜴦𜵎⎻𜴧🬭▂</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">        ▁▂𜴧━𜵼𜵶𜶮▂🬭🬭𜴐🭗  🬁𜴜🬭🬭▂𜶮▁𜵁━𜴧▂▁</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">     𜷓𜵐🬂🬂🮂𜶮𜴸𜴪━𜴆🮂▔        ▔🮂𜴆━𜴩𜵳𜴸🮂🬂🬂𜶚🬿</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">    🭄🬨▍ 🬜🮂▔      ▁▂▂🬭🬭▂▂▁      ▔🮂🬪 🮈🬕𜶿</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">   🭄🭙▐▎𜵫       🭃██████████🭎      🭢𜶡🮇▌🭤𜶿</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">  🭄🭙 ▐🭄🭙      🭋█████🭜𜴦█████🭀      🭤🭏▌ 🭤🭏</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\"> 𜵫🭗  🮉🭛       🭃███🭝🭙  🭥🭒███🭎       🭦▋  🭢𜶡</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">▟🬮𜴧━🭷🭘       🭋████▄▂  ▂▄████🭀       🭣𜴇━𜴧🬯🭏</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">🭕𜴸𜴆╾🭺🬽       🭃██🭡        🭖██🭐       🭈𜵡╼𜴆🬡🭠</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\"> 𜴤🬼  🮉🭀     🭋███΄        🭤███🭀     🭋▊  🭇𜵐</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">  𜴠🬾 ▐𜴢🬾▁▁  🭃██𜴍          𜶘██🭐  ▁▁🭉🭫▌ 🭉🭠</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">   𜴠🬾🮈▎𜶚 ▔🮂🬂▀🬎🬎            🮅🬎▀🬂🮂▔ 𜵐🮇▌🭉𜴏</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">    𜴢🭿▍ 𜴬▂▁                    ▁▂🬜΄🮈🬲𜴏</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">     🭥𜶡🬭🬭▂𜶭▁𜵁━𜴧▂▁        ▁▂𜴧━𜶷𜶭𜶮▂🬭🬭𜵫🭚</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">        ▔⎺𜴆━𜴩▔𜶮🮂🬂🬂𜴜🬼  🭇𜴐🬂🬂🮂𜶮▔𜴨━𜴆⎺▔</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4\">              ⠈🮂🭷𜴆╾𜶦𜷞🭄𜴬╼𜴆🬂🮂΄</span>",
